## 7. GML Code Examples

### Check if accessibility is enabled

```gml
if (variable_global_exists("a11y_enabled") && global.a11y_enabled) {
    tw_output("text to announce", 1);
}
```

### Announce with duplicate prevention

```gml
if (global.a11y_enabled) {
    var _text = [GET CURRENT TEXT];
    if (_text != global.a11y_last_text) {
        global.a11y_last_text = _text;
        tw_output(_text, 1);
    }
}
```

### Read menu item

```gml
if (global.a11y_enabled && keyboard_check_pressed(vk_up) || keyboard_check_pressed(vk_down)) {
    var _item = [GET MENU ITEM TEXT AT CURRENT INDEX];
    tw_output(_item, 1);
}
```

